title: VA Indie Pop Playlist September 2013 - I1 Delicate (Dutch Treat)
description:
Already the first Indie playlist from September and immediately an I1 list. 

 Thanks to my imaginary "Best Indie" friend from PB, I had a very nice weekend. It's nice to meet an idiot like myself. Some recognition maybe. Anyway we listened to some thousand songs. Most were beautiful, some clearly good and some were just to good to keep quiet. So I put these songs in my September lists (although most of them are a bit older but you might have missed them too). But whatever reason; in my ears, the list is quite special as it is. The songs really support each other. All in XHQ.


Could not wait to put it on the net..... Enjoy,
